                	The paper should start with an introduction and should end with a conclusion summarizing the findings of the paper. </br>
                	If papers were presented/submitted in a conference/seminar or are minor / major research project, this must be clearly mentioned in the first page of the manuscript clearly.  Manuscripts, including tables, figures and references should be around 4000-5000 words, in the case of articles and 1000 words for book reviews. </br>
